      <title>伊斯兰债券违约风险迫在眉睫，印度准备向马尔代夫提供援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/india-ready-to-give-maldives-aid-as-sukuk-default-risk-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，在马尔代夫面临首笔伊斯兰债券违约风险之际，印度政府已准备好向马尔代夫提供紧急财政援助，以帮助缓解该岛国的财政困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/india-ready-to-give-maldives-aid-as-sukuk-default-risk-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 09:02:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称东京地铁将于下周公布 IPO 计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/tokyo-metro-is-said-to-unveil-700-billion-yen-ipo-plan-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，东京地铁公司预计将于 9 月 20 日公布其首次公开募股计划的细节，该计划可能使该公司的估值达到约 7000 亿日元（50 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/tokyo-metro-is-said-to-unveil-700-billion-yen-ipo-plan-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 08:34:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受风暴和风险偏好影响，油价有望录得一个月来首周涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在风暴弗朗辛扰乱原油生产后，油价有望在一个月内首次周度上涨，风险偏好情绪席卷了整个市场，有助于缓解此前超卖的原油市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 23:28:12 GMT</pubDate>
